descriptionHtml:
HARBIN is the newest platform on the ride-hailling apps world. whether you are a taxi driver, VTC driver, carpooler, transporter, full-timer or occasionally, you own a car and want to easily earn extra cash, join us !

Unlike Yassir, Careem, TemTem, Heetch, Coursa, Amir… available in Algeria, where the price and commission are imposed on you, with HARBIN you are free, work easily, without exclusivity and above all without ANY commission.
Be your own boss: You define your price and your own schedule, it’s YOU who decides.

How does it work ?
Download the HARBIN App.
Manually configure your driver session (you can create several).
Select the transport request that interests you from your transporter space or directly on the Map and send your offer.
Make the ride and keep 100% of your win!
You can also run the “auto-bid” feature, it will send automatic offers to you clients, depending on the recorded price on your configurator.

How does Harbin earn money:
At Harbin the drivers get to win 100% of their rides costs.
How do we earn money ?
-Through advertising
-Points purchase required to increase your income and visibility.

Community:

Harbin is a platform that brings together different drivers and clients, where togetherness comes first and sharing is an important value to all.
HARBIN, Choose a new way to move.
descriptionShort: VTC, TAXI, the only transportation application at 0% commission.
